    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《开关盒》是一款2D像素风格平台解谜游戏。玩家需在未知世界中巧妙利用环境与道具，解开谜题，克服重重障碍，最终找到回家的路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目标是开拓前方的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/3a9f73b4d7143e440b2e77ccf33230a5.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/3a9f73b4d7143e440b2e77ccf33230a5.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/3a9f73b4d7143e440b2e77ccf33230a5.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用身边的道具通过障碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/e538d587cee997eb044fdcc3ed84a0b2.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/e538d587cee997eb044fdcc3ed84a0b2.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/e538d587cee997eb044fdcc3ed84a0b2.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找准时机向前出发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/59fbefc81a04fc5e0ec740bea5cdb25d.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/59fbefc81a04fc5e0ec740bea5cdb25d.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/59fbefc81a04fc5e0ec740bea5cdb25d.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打开开关向前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/036d4ec20841a0ebee1b681dd567c62f.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/036d4ec20841a0ebee1b681dd567c62f.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/036d4ec20841a0ebee1b681dd567c62f.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >意料之中，意料之外。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/f683e8eb877fa963e3f6bc069f0019b3.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/f683e8eb877fa963e3f6bc069f0019b3.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/f683e8eb877fa963e3f6bc069f0019b3.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >危险之中探寻前路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/5989fea578212f0a46a568f78f9a47a1.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/5989fea578212f0a46a568f78f9a47a1.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/5989fea578212f0a46a568f78f9a47a1.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成目标到达下一个舞台。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/48015406a9f81eebad0daf64e4bf2f85.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/48015406a9f81eebad0daf64e4bf2f85.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/48015406a9f81eebad0daf64e4bf2f85.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
